# Copy to `.env` (which is git-ignored) and fill in ONLY if you use optional
# keyed features. The default data path is KEYLESS (yfinance / Stooq / Hacker
# News / Yahoo RSS), so a fresh clone runs with NO secrets at all.
#
# No secret in this file is real. Nothing here is ever written into a produced
# artifact (HTML/XLSX/PPTX/DOCX) — see docs/00-overview.md §8.

# --- Agent backend (P5, optional). Only needed for live LLM curation. ---
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# --- Optional premium market/news sources (not required). ---
# ALPHAVANTAGE_API_KEY=
# NEWSAPI_KEY=
